Population of this collection should only occur from the stock
order side when an order line is matched
Instances of CM_BOLOutStockOrderLineTI are never created in the creation of a bolOut</text>
        <Inverse name="CM_BOLOutStockOrderLineTI::myBOLOut"/>
    </ExplicitInverseRef>
